description: Test E2E Scenario from Login to create a New Reservation with valid unit and guest

steps.name: Wait for Captcha to be verified
Verify Successful Login to Dashboard page
Click on the Later and Close buttons to close popups
Verify Navigated to Add Reservation page successfully
Select first option from Reservation Source dropdown
Verify the Select Unit popup is displayed
Click on the Confirm button after selecting the valid unit
Verify the valid Unit Number is selected successfully: 17
Click on the Select Guest Now button
Click on Search button to find guest
Hover over the guest name to select
Verify Reservation is Created successfully with ID: 123456789
